[b]---> YES THIS IS MY SERVER MY OTHER NAME IS DUHPK BUT THESE STAFF MEMBERS REFUSE TO HELP ME RECOVER MY OTHER FORUMS ACCOUNT BECAUSE I NO LONGER HAVE ACCESS TO MY EMAIL FOR THAT ACCOUNT <---[/b] [i]I wanted to respost it on an account I could log into[/i]
[b]This release is a release of the Beta version of Drowning508, which means there is MANY bugs/glitches that need to be fixed by YOU, there is no anti leech if you compile there should be no errors but I warn you this contains many bugs and is not suitable to be hosted as an actual server as soon as the download is complete, a lot of work was put into this but it needs more from you.[/b] [B] It has many features I do not want to list them all so just look @ the pictures.[/B] --- How to fix the GE prices: In geloader.java Search for [code]FileReader fr[/code] Replace that whole line with [code]FileReader fr = new FileReader("data/items/grandExchange.cfg");[/code] ---
